OL,3,CTeacup ride malfunction at Dreamland
OL,4,Cleaves mother and daughter injured
OL,6,FA mother and her three-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter are recovering at home after
OL,8,Fbeing injured when a teacup ride
OL,9,Fmalfunctioned at Dreamland, in Margate.
OL,11,FKate Davies and her daughter, Poppy,
OL,12,Fsay the spinning teacup they were
OL,13,Fsitting in detached from its base and
OL,14,Fsent them crashing into railings.
OL,16,FThey were given immediate care by
OL,17,Ffirst-aiders on site.
