OL,3,CTeacup ride malfunction at Dreamland
OL,4,Cleaves mother and daughter injured
OL,6,FWilliam Davies, Poppy's father, said:
OL,7,F"We've never been to Margate so we
OL,8,Fthought we'd go give it a go, so the
OL,9,Fkids could go on some rides and have a
OL,10,Ffun day out."
OL,12,FMrs Davies said: "We were on the ride
OL,13,Fand it was going ok and the next
OL,14,Fminute we knew, as we went past and we
OL,15,Fwere spun, the entire teacup that we
OL,16,Fwere sitting in, just detached.
OL,18,F"Came completely off the ride, and
OL,19,Fcrashed into the barrier, into
OL,20,Frailings, by the gate. "
