OL,3,CTeacup ride malfunction at Dreamland
OL,4,Cleaves mother and daughter injured
OL,6,FMr Davies said: "I just heard
OL,7,Fscreaming and a massive thud, and the
OL,8,Fteacup was just upside down."
OL,10,FThe family want to make people aware
OL,11,Fof what happened to them, and make
OL,12,Fsure there is accountability and
OL,13,Fsafety measures put in place.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Dreamland said: "On
OL,16,FWednesday (31 July) an incident
OL,17,Foccurred on the cups and saucers
OL,18,Fattraction, one of the rides for
OL,19,Fyounger visitors at Dreamland Margate,
OL,20,FKent.
