OL,4,Cleaves mother and daughter injured
OL,6,F"Dreamland's standard safety
OL,7,Fprocedures were put in place, overseen
OL,8,Fby the Park Manager. The family was
OL,9,Fchecked over and given immediate care
OL,10,Fby the qualified first aiders on site.
OL,12,F"A member of senior management from
OL,13,FDreamland has been in touch with the
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,F"The cups and saucer attraction has
OL,17,Fbeen repaired and certified safe for
OL,18,Fuse and the family have been invited
OL,19,Fto return to Dreamland at a time of
OL,20,Ftheir choice.
